  <!-- Section: Application Process -->
  <section id="application" class="scroll-mt-24 mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Application Process</h2>

    <p class="mb-4">
      The Active Investor Plus application involves an Expression of Interest (EOI), followed by an Invitation to Apply (ITA) if your EOI is successful. Processing times are typically 3-6 months, but can be longer for complex applications.
    </p>

    <ComparisonTable columns={timelineColumns} rows={timelineRows} />

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-3">Step-by-Step Guide: Active Investor Plus</h3>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">1</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Verify Eligibility and Prepare</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Confirm you meet investment threshold and English requirements. Engage a licensed immigration adviser in New Zealand—this is mandatory for complex applications. Prepare documentation of investment funds and their legal source.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">2</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Submit Expression of Interest (EOI)</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Submit EOI through Immigration New Zealand's online system. Include details of proposed investment, business background, and how you'll contribute to NZ's economic growth. Fee applies. EOIs are assessed periodically.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">3</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Receive Invitation to Apply (ITA)</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">If your EOI is successful, you'll receive an ITA within 2-3 months. You then have a set timeframe (usually 4 months) to submit your full application with all supporting documents.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">4</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Compile Full Application</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Gather all required documents: passport, police certificates, health examinations, proof of funds, bank statements, investment plan, English test results, and character references. Most documents need to be certified or apostilled.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">5</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Submit Full Application</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Submit complete application online through Immigration NZ. Pay the application fee (NZD 4,310 + levy). Include detailed investment proposal showing how funds will be deployed in qualifying investments.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">6</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Application Assessment</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Immigration NZ assesses your application, verifies funds source, checks character and health, and evaluates your investment plan. They may request additional information. Processing typically takes 3-6 months.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">7</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Visa Approval and Fund Transfer</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Upon approval, you receive your investor visa (valid 4 years). You must transfer your investment funds to qualifying NZ investments within 12 months of approval. Work with NZ fund managers and investment advisors to deploy capital appropriately.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">8</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Investment Period and Residence</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Maintain your qualifying investment for 4 years. Immigration NZ will verify your investment periodically. After the 4-year period, apply for residence. You can then access public healthcare and work toward citizenship (after 5 years residence).</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-4 mt-6">
      <p class="text-blue-800">
        <strong>Entrepreneur Work Visa process:</strong> The Entrepreneur pathway follows a similar EOI-ITA structure but focuses on your business plan rather than investment capital. You'll need to demonstrate how your business will benefit New Zealand through job creation, innovation, or export growth. Points are awarded for factors like capital amount, business experience, and age.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

