        <p class="text-green-700 font-medium">Entrepreneur Work Visa approved after demonstrating high-value IT services business plan. Invested NZD 150K, employing 4 NZ staff after 18 months. Southern Cross insurance (NZD 280/month). Working toward Entrepreneur Resident Visa—business exceeding growth projections. Notes NZ clients appreciate timezone for APAC markets.</p>
