        <p class="text-red-700 font-medium">Application rejected—government bonds no longer qualify under Active Investor Plus. Post-2022 rules require "active" investments in growth assets. Redirected to NZ managed funds investing in growth companies. Re-applied 6 months later with qualifying investment portfolio. Now approved and tracking toward residence. Key lesson: Understand the 2022 rule changes before applying.</p>
